h1. execSync{} 

h2. Purpose

Executes a block of code by making a synchronous call inside the UI Thread.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
class SampleController {
    def action = { evt = null ->
        execSync { model.value = 'some immediate update' }
    }
}
{code}

h2. Description

See the [threading|guide:threading] section for more information about this method and others like it.
